'''天主教恩卡伊教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Nkayiensis}}；{{lang-fr|Diocèse de Nkayi}}）是[[剛果共和國|剛果共和國]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教區，屬[[天主教黑角總教區|黑角總教區]]<ref name="Vatican20200530">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 30.05.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/05/30/200530b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-05-30 |language=en |date=2020-05-30 |archivedate=2020-05-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200530165042/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/05/30/200530b.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

教區於1983年12月5日成立<ref>{{cite web |title=NKAYENSIS* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19831205_nkayensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2020-05-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531093647/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19831205_nkayensis.html |archivedate=2020-05-31 |language=la |date=1983-12-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，管轄[[布恩扎省|布恩扎省]]和[[萊庫穆省|萊庫穆省]]，教座位於布恩扎省首府[[恩卡伊|恩卡伊]]。

教區於2020年時有35萬3700名教友（佔轄區總人口60.8%）、16個[[堂區|堂區]]和38名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。<ref name="Vatican20200530" />現任教區主教為{{link-fr|達尼爾·米宗佐|Daniel Mizonzo}}，榮休主教為{{link-fr|伯爾納鐸·恩薩伊|Bernard Nsayi}}。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Entry into force of the Framework Agreement between the Holy See and the Republic of the Congo on the relations between the Catholic Church and the State, 02.07.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/02/190703d.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-05-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531101450/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/02/190703d.html |archivedate=2020-05-31 |language=en |date=2019-07-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

